This is the step by step process of this tableau sales and customer insight visualization project.

** STEP 1: Requirement analysis **
          ⦁	Collect requirements
          ⦁	Choose right charts
          ⦁	Draw mockups
          ⦁	Choose colours

** STEP 2: Build Data Source ( Missing, null and other problems in the data is checked with the help of Tableau Prep) **
          ⦁	Connect data
          ⦁	Create data model
          ⦁	Rename fields and tables
          ⦁	Check data types
          ⦁	Understand data

** STEP 3: Build Charts **
          ⦁	Create calculated fields & test
          ⦁	Build chart
          ⦁	Format
           	- Remove lines & grids
           	- Clean up axis & headers
           	- Colouring
           	- Tooltips

** STEP 4: Build Dashboard **
          ⦁	Draw mockup for container
          ⦁	Create container structure
          ⦁	Put all charts together
          ⦁	Format
           	- Distribute object evenly
           	- Format colours, size, ... etc
           	- Fit "Entire view"
           	- Add legends
           	- Add spaces (Inner & outer padding)
          ⦁	Add filters & dynamic
          ⦁	Add icons
